# Local secrets / env. Secret-bearing env files (.env, .dev.vars, secrets.env) are
# ignored. The two exceptions below are Vite VITE_* files that get inlined into the
# browser bundle - they are PUBLIC by design (cannot hold secrets) and are committed
# on purpose. Real secrets go in .dev.vars (ignored) or `wrangler secret put`.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.development
!.env.production

